OL,3,CHow to stay safe in the water during
OL,4,Cwarm weather
OL,6,FExperts are warning about the dangers
OL,7,Fof open water swimming, following a
OL,8,Fnumber of deaths over the May Bank
OL,9,FHoliday weekend.
OL,11,FAs England and Wales recorded the
OL,12,Fhottest May day ever, many Brits took
OL,13,Fto the water to cool off.
OL,15,FBut several children and one man
OL,16,Fdrowned in separate incidents across
OL,17,Fthe country after entering bodies of
OL,18,Fwater.
OL,20,FSo how can you stay safe around water
OL,21,Fin extreme heat? ITV News explains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
