OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779951883
OL,3,CHow to stay safe in the water during
OL,4,Cwarm weather
OL,6,FProfessor Mike Tipton, chair of the
OL,7,FNational Water Safety Forum, told Good
OL,8,FMorning Britain that deaths from
OL,9,Fdrowning are an "enormous problem"
OL,10,Fwhich disproportionately affects
OL,11,Fyounger people, particularly those
OL,12,Funder 40.
OL,14,FWith 85% of drowning victims being
OL,15,Fmale, especially men aged 20 to 29,
OL,16,FProfessor Tipton said it was vital
OL,17,Fthat safety messages reached this
OL,18,Fgroup, who were more likely to take
OL,19,Frisks and enter bodies of water.
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
