OL,3,CHow to stay safe in the water during
OL,4,Cwarm weather
OL,6,FThe cold shock response usually lasts
OL,7,Faround a minute, and surviving that
OL,8,Finitial period significantly improves
OL,9,Fthe chances of survival.
OL,11,FThe RNLI also recommends that if you
OL,12,Fenter cold water unexpectedly, you
OL,13,Fshould:
OL,15,FIf you are planning to go into the
OL,16,Fwater:
OL,18,FWhat is "Float to Live"?
