OL,3,CHow to stay safe in the water during
OL,4,Cwarm weather
OL,6,FThe RNLI's "Float to Live" advice is a
OL,7,Fsurvival technique designed to help
OL,8,Fpeople stay alive in whatever
OL,9,Fcircumstances they find themselves in.
OL,11,FThe charity says it has helped save
OL,12,Fmore than 50 lives in situations
OL,13,Franging from rip currents and canal
OL,14,Ffalls to people being swept out by
OL,15,Fwaves or falling overboard.
OL,17,FThe method is:
OL,19,FOnce your breathing is under control,
OL,20,Fyou can call for help or swim to
OL,21,Fsafety if you are able.
OL,26,@nD@LOUnD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
