OL,3,CHow to stay safe in the water during
OL,4,Cwarm weather
OL,6,FThe RNLI also recommends practising
OL,7,Ffloating in places like a swimming
OL,8,Fpool, so the technique becomes normal
OL,9,Fto you before it is ever needed in an
OL,10,Femergency.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FWhat are the risks of swimming in open
OL,18,Fwater?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
