OL,3,CHow to stay safe in the water during
OL,4,Cwarm weather
OL,6,FThe RNLI warns that open water can be
OL,7,Funpredictable and dangerous, with
OL,8,Fhazards including unstable ground,
OL,9,Fcold water, and hidden currents.
OL,11,FTo reduce risk on land:
OL,13,FWhat should I do at the beach?
OL,15,FThe RNLI advises choosing beaches with
OL,16,Flifeguards in summer and swimming
OL,17,Fbetween the red and yellow flags.
OL,19,FBefore entering the water:
OL,21,FWhen entering:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
