PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779951883
OL,3,CHow to stay safe in the water during
OL,4,Cwarm weather
OL,6,FWhat if someone else is in danger?
OL,8,FThe RNLI advises calling 999 or 112
OL,9,Fand asking for the coastguard. If
OL,10,Fpossible, throw something that floats
OL,11,For that the person can hold onto.
OL,13,FDo not enter the water yourself, as
OL,14,Fmany drownings happen when people
OL,15,Fattempt rescues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
